query:
SELECT
                COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '1 hour') as "last_hour!: i64",
                COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '24 hours') as "last_24h!: i64",
                COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '7 days') as "last_7d!: i64"
            FROM games
